&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Medical Secretary – Respiratory – 37.5 AfC Band 4 – Internal Applicants Only Please &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have highly effective secretarial and organisational skills and enjoy supporting a team, we have an exciting opportunity for you! We are looking for a Lead Medical Secretary to join our Respiratory team who is able to efficiently support our consultants, lead and coordinate our current administrative staff and communicate effectively and compassionately with our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous secretarial experience with excellent typing skills is essential; experience in the medical setting or of medical terminology is desirable, but not necessary. This is a busy department therefore the ability to “think on your feet”, prioritise to meet deadlines and be a calming influence on the team is a key part of the role. Our ideal candidate will be flexible and adaptable and excited to support our secretarial staff to ensure the team is working as effectively as possible. If you think you have the qualities to fill this post then we would like to hear from you! Training and support will be given to the successful candidate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To arrange an informal chat about the role, please do get in contact with Jordan Snell via email: max.warner-holt@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
